{"tid":1777385,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"妻兒遭人騙進深山還生3胎…10年後被警方找到！丈夫竟絕望變成「女生」","createTime":"2019-12-10T07:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T08:16:33.000Z","uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5e93b6de53789ce49b593033171b5edfded24092","tid":1777385,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:45:10.000Z","msg":"記者陳雕文／綜合報導<br />\n北部一對平凡夫妻結婚後育有一子，沒想到妻兒遭人誘拐，從此音訊全無，丈夫苦尋10年！後來警方發現妻兒在沒水沒電的山區裡跟友人生活，這段日子裡還生了3名兒女；人夫與兒子重逢後察覺兩人長得不像，驗了DNA才知他並非親生&hellip;找到妻兒應該要開心的，卻是這種結果，人夫絕望「變性」成為女生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4567/d4567642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4567%2Fd4567642.jpg&h=d69b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲丈夫得知殘酷真相後變性，令人不勝唏噓。（示意圖，非新聞當事人／記者陳雕文翻攝）"},{"pid":"8e04ecaa5c99aa25121e67b86643a35b80656aac","tid":1777385,"uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"看似平凡的小家庭卻走了樣&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2008年，輕度智能障礙的人妻花花（化名）抱著兒子在街上散步，巧遇老公的朋友阿倫（化名），阿倫見花花單純可愛，竟言語誘拐母子跟他走，並扮演起丈夫的角色，開始三人的「山居生活」；老公找不到妻小，心急如焚瘋狂找尋，怎麼也沒想到，自己已經被取代。<br />\n<br />\n就這樣過了10年&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n警方在去年於一處深山裡發現了「一家6口」，4個瘦到剩皮包骨的孩子看了令人心疼；據了解，孩子們若是飢餓，大多時間只能開水「喝到飽」，並睡在厚紙板上，在沒水沒電又散發濃烈異味的惡劣環境下生存。<br />\n<br />\n承辦警員解釋，「這些小朋友都沒有離開過那個地方，開巡邏車載他們下山時，每個人都吐得亂七八糟；他們對任何食物都感到新奇，拿到什麼（食物）就不斷往嘴裡塞。」後來通報社會局介入，協助安置並報戶口，讓孩子們可以開始上學。<br />\n<br />\n他成了「她」<br />\n<br />\n承辦警員表示，妻小離開這麼多年，老公拼命尋找&hellip;好不容易發現人，得知老婆是被朋友誘拐還生了孩子，更令人難過的是，原先花花幫他生的兒子，居然也不是自己親生的。晴天霹靂的打擊，讓他就此崩潰&hellip;為了逃離殘酷的現實，他決定變性&hellip;透過手術讓自己重獲新生，不要再跟眼前的人有任何瓜葛。承辦警員說，妻小都找到後不久，再看到人夫已成了女生，令人不勝唏噓。"},{"pid":"eeb2ad167392e5fa737e8c4fb46e7bf572c972be","tid":1777385,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedd30b4863a8be23612ff6a96c42c4b8b7468c4","tid":1777385,"uid":15644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:47:15.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49a4daa8e632fa8fbb737768ad02b9c631cbe43","tid":1777385,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"又喺台灣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf6667a6eb9332cd013a47c5877ccdbeb221c87","tid":1777385,"uid":36774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:50:41.000Z","msg":"屌 乜撚嘢新聞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab17339a4810a5c0e94efd7c6942bc43e22abc2","tid":1777385,"uid":153087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53bb9f7bc6282d1ba249daf468bf19e6c6d6747a","tid":1777385,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:01:22.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f40ef222b298dffdcb638971a76ac263a947057","tid":1777385,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6160a653b2b5fabe67cadc5dcc0cd40fc1bbae5d","tid":1777385,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji